      "description": "Phase 5 adds **no new REST endpoints** — it runs work asynchronously via Celery.\n\n## Async emails (console backend in dev → printed in worker logs)\n- **Welcome email** — fired by `Auth → Register` and `Members → Invite member`.\n- **Deal-won email** — fired by `Deals → Move deal to stage` when the target stage is **Won**.\n\nStart the workers and watch them run:\n```bash\ndocker compose up -d celery-worker celery-beat\ndocker compose logs -f celery-worker\n```\n\n## Scheduled job\n`flag_stale_leads` runs daily via Celery Beat and sets `is_stale=true` on cold open leads. The result is visible on the Lead API (see the request below).",
